          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/17881790/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/17881790/" class="">第4页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/icefish0816/" class=" " title="-ECHO-Liu">-ECHO-Liu</a>
                (做最真实的自己！)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="17881790">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">然富者不足，强者不安，而安足者又不富强。

人身非滋养则不能生长，文化非刺激则不能持续而发展。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-04-19 15:56</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
